&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;At &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hear.com/&quot;&gt;hear.com&lt;/a&gt;, we believe that &lt;strong&gt;everyone should hear well to live well&lt;/strong&gt;. Our mission is to bring high quality hearing care to anyone, anywhere, and to change our customers’ lives through better hearing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
